snippet.title: Shifty’s Back… ALRIGHT | Fortnite OG Season 2 Returns January 31
snippet.description: Grab your glider and drop into Fortnite OG Season 2! We're bringing back beloved POIs, a vintage loot pool, and an all-new OG Pass. Jump back in and experience it all for yourself.
